headline: Arch Capital Group Ltd. to Report 2025 Second Quarter Results on July 29
summary: PEMBROKE, Bermuda, June 25, 2025--Arch Capital Group Ltd. (NASDAQ: ACGL) ("Arch" or the "Company") today announced it expects to release its 2025 second quarter results after the close of regular stock market hours on Tuesday, July 29. The Company will hold a conference call for investors and analysts at 10:00 a.m. ET on Wednesday, July 30.
